attack or
defending someone who was.

44:37.875 --> 44:42.246 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Wesley Lowery was one of The
Washington Post's
lead reporters on this. He's
part of a team

44:42.346 --> 44:45.650 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
