45:13.611 --> 45:17.248 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WESLEY LOWERY: So, this idea,
this project
was born in a lot of ways out of
Ferguson,

45:17.348 --> 45:19.150 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
