about it,
race, age, gender, mental
illness, for example.

46:41.198 --> 46:42.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Whether they were
armed or
not.

46:43.034 --> 46:44.535 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WESLEY LOWERY: Whether they were
