46:56.347 --> 46:58.115 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But this was a year's worth of
reporting.

46:58.215 --> 47:03.654 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: It really made a
