47:15.800 --> 47:17.034 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Did that surprise
you?

47:17.134 --> 47:18.936 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WESLEY LOWERY: No, that wasn't
